<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Activate to use the Callisto URL route pattern in Ceres. This is required, for example, when using the <a href="/en/omni-channel/online-store/best-practices#checkout">Ceres checkout in Callisto</a>.</p></td>
