<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select one, multiple or <strong>ALL</strong> contact information options to be displayed in the contact data in the online store. The contact information activated here are loaded from the <a href="#basics/first-steps/master-data">master data</a> of your plentymarkets system.</p></td>
</tr>
