→ The plugin overview opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Ceres</strong>.<br>
→ The plugin opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Configuration</strong> in the directory tree.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on the <strong>Item lists</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the settings. Pay attention to the information given in <a href="#table-item-lists">Table 8</a>.</p>
</li>
