<div class="sect3">
<h4 id="220">1.7.4. Setting online store languages</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Carry out language settings in the <strong>Languages</strong> tab. By default <strong>Ceres</strong> is available in German and English. Select these languages in the header area of your online store. <strong>Ceres</strong> supports all plentymarkets system languages. You can <a href="#231">translate</a> your online store and your items into other languages.</p>
</div>
<div id="230" class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Setting up online store languages:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
