<p>Configure the settings as described in <a href="#table-automatic-order-confirmation">Table 17</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Place a check mark next to the option <strong>Active</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> the settings.</p>
</li>
